Sideline 2015 heads to Creekside at Bartram Trail Sideline 2015 heads to Creekside at Bartram Trail Post to Facebook Sideline 2015 heads to Creekside at Bartram Trail Sideline 2015 heads to Creekside at Bartram Trail  //fcnews.tv/1FK4vHh   Join the Conversation To   Sideline 2015 heads to Creekside at Bartram Trail Courtney Jones, Sports MMJ/Producer 12:11 a.m. EDT October 2, 2015 #Teamsideline 3 CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
Week 6 of Sideline 2015 takes the First Coast Sports team to St. John's County for the Game of the Week. It's Creekside (0-5) at Bartram Trail (3-2) as both teams open up district play. 
Our "Game of the Week" coverage starts Friday afternoon at 5 and continues at 5:30, 6, 7, and 11. 
If Creekside and Bartram Trail doesn't tickle your fancy, fear not. The First Coast Sports team will have cameras at games all across the First Coast so you won't miss any of the hard-hitting action. Tune in to Sideline 2015 for all of the Week 6 action, Friday night at 11:15 p.m.
